{"tid":1493146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[環保L] 反對犧牲九龍公園生態起地下空間商場 - 今日截止!!!","createTime":"2019-08-21T06:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T09:34:55.000Z","uid":271529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b79d4d19cc744a645cbcd4eb5dddbbc34fe95e","tid":1493146,"uid":271529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://protectkowloonpark.weebly.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprotectkowloonpark.weebly.com%2F&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9ovvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=d197eaab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://protectkowloonpark.weebly.com/</a><br />\n九龍公園下建設地下空間簡介, 反對理由及Template. <br />\n內有Template, 不過根據上次反DQ話Template唔認數, 大家最好可以自己去土木工程署個諮詢頁親自填. <br />\n可參考上文的理由, 我也將我自己填寫的理由貼上來, 大家可以參考. <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.urbanunderground.gov.hk/public_engagement2.php?locale=tc#!\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urbanunderground.gov.hk%2Fpublic_engagement2.php%3Flocale%3Dtc%23%21&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9ovvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=e4fb4d05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.urbanunderground.gov.hk/public_engagement2.php?locale=tc#!</a><br />\n土木工程署諮詢網頁, D問題係好誘導性, 可以睇得出佢其實已經準備做, 諮詢不過係咁&quot;二&quot;. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 您對擬議的九龍公園地下行人連接在尖沙咀地區的行人連接性有甚麼意見？(可選多項)<br />\nv沒有需要改善尖沙咀地區現有的行人連接性<br />\n<br />\nv其他: <br />\n工程所涉及的挖掘面積約33,250平方米，佔九龍公園面積的25%，而大部分的土地目前被大樹覆蓋。本人擔心工程將對這些樹木的健康和生存造成損害，進而干擾鳥類的棲息和覓食地。<br />\n2. 您對擬議的九龍公園地下行人連接在尖沙咀地區的行人步行體驗有甚麼意見？(可選多項)<br />\nv 沒有需要透過擬議的地下空間來改善尖沙咀地區的步行體驗<br />\n因為: <br />\n尖沙咀周邊已經夠多行人路,日常市民也可以穿過九龍公園內四通八達的路到其他地區.現在鳥語花香的環境已經是很好的步行體驗, 地下空間徒有四壁如何改善步行體驗?<br />\nv 其他: <br />\n地下空間勢必需要更多冷氣系統而導致溫室效應加劇. <br />\n擬議用途<br />\n3. 您認為擬議的九龍公園地下空間應該有甚麼設施？(可選多項)<br />\nv 其他: <br />\n不應建設九龍公園地下空間.<br />\n4. 您對擬議的用途分佈有甚麼意見？(可選多項)<br />\nv 其他: <br />\n不應建設九龍公園地下空間.<br />\n施工計劃考慮<br />\n5. 您認為應以單階段還是分階段方式發展擬議的九龍公園地下空間？ <br />\n&lt;這題我兩個選項都無選, 都可以提交到&gt;<br />\n其他意見<br />\n6. 您有其他意見和建議嗎？<br />\n不應建設九龍公園地下空間<br />\n個人資料 &lt;--填自己個人資料."},{"pid":"dac1b303efedfbf1b2ab3bb4725d33a7062d2246","tid":1493146,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:37:13.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa47b4f47cbef02bfcc69847c894b7f48548499","tid":1493146,"uid":271529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never<br />\n<br />\n612<br />\n721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"41faa95024ace58a2f0570186854e89f42452978","tid":1493146,"uid":26449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:32:14.000Z","msg":"已填"},{"pid":"6a80c9d5915f89c61e717786685780bd7e6f3f6a","tid":1493146,"uid":62285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"推!  大家快d 反對!"},{"pid":"8073655750a95221133ad693086376eeb3c561f7","tid":1493146,"uid":191052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:00:37.000Z","msg":"已填 小心第五條 香港加油"},{"pid":"70addc0928de532d7527a8211becbf1c6e23eceb","tid":1